. programming on Linux
 . dj delorie website provides a tool to program the kit: rxusb
  . http://www.delorie.com/electronics/rx-stick
  . instruction to be followed:
   . http://www.renesasrulz.com/thread/3137
  . originally done for th ethe rx-stick board that needed a kernel patch
  . plus there is no serial interface in the new rx kit

 . opensource software and toolchains
  . http://www.rxmcu.com/USA/software.php
  . http://www.kpitgnutools.com/index.php
  . https://github.com/nullsub/RX62n-media
