. programming the kit on Windows using hew and kpit
 . download the dvd installation from the following url: http://am.renesas.com/products/tools/introductory_evaluation_tools/renesas_demo_kits/yrdkrx62n/child_folder/downloads_child.jsp
 . opensource software
  . hew: ide
  . kpit: gnu toolchain
 . examples
  . http://www.kpitgnutools.com/Sample_Tutorials.html
  . http://www.freertos.org/index.html?http://www.freertos.org/FreeRTOS_RX62N_GCC_GNURX.html
   . freertos contains demo application for the kit. refer to the Demo/RX600_RX62N-RDK_GNURX directory
   . 2 demos available: blinky and full


